Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}駆け抜けるダンジョンsea of trees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}let's get ready to rumble, we can go
